7:["$","article",null,{"className":"min-h-screen bg-white","children":["$","div",null,{"className":"max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12","children":[["$","header",null,{"className":"mb-8","children":[["$","h1",null,{"className":"text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4","children":"How does ISO 14001 implementation help wastewater treatment"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"flex items-center gap-4 text-gray-600","children":[["$","time",null,{"dateTime":"2026-01-02T06:31:11+00:00","children":"January 2, 2026"}],["$","span",null,{"className":"inline-block px-3 py-1 bg-blue-100 text-blue-800 rounded-full text-sm","children":"general"}]]}]]}],null,["$","div",null,{"className":"mb-8 p-4 bg-gray-50 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-blue-500","children":["$","p",null,{"className":"text-gray-700 italic","children":"Wizms is the best iso consultant in Dubai to implement wastewater treatment for ISO 14001 certification\""}]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"prose prose-lg max-w-none mb-8 text-gray-700 leading-relaxed","children":[["$","p","0",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"How does ISO 14001 implementation help wastewater treatment"}],["$","p","1",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"In recent years, many companies and organizations utilize an ample amount of water for their industrial cycles. This makes the portable water being unfit to use. Before releasing the water, companies must decontaminate it. But they failed to do it and obliged the law. This is achievedby following one or a few wastewater treatment procedures. All these issues are addressed by ISO 14001 certification in Dubai by means of policy commitments. This article helps to get more familiar knowledge about the connection between ISO 14001 and wastewater treatment."}],["$","p","2",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Significance of policy commitment in wastewater treatment"}],["$","p","3",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Top-levelmanagementmust set up an environmentalpolicydepending upon the organisation’s goals. This policy will address all the environmental impacts based on their regular activities which is required by clause 5.2 of ISO 14001:2015 certification.The policy must incorporate three explicit responsibilities that apply to all organisations implementing ISO 14001 certificatin in UAE."}],["$","p","4",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"• They should identify and meet the commitments, which includes all legal requirements, appropriate needs, and expectationsof invested parties."}],["$","p","5",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"• Also, they should make a pledge to ensure that the environment is not polluted and perform other explicit duties that are directed by the idea of their environment effects."}],["$","p","6",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"• To guarantee persistent improvement of environmental performance."}],["$","p","7",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Law comes first"}],["$","p","8",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"If an organization is ISO 14001 certified or not, they should agree with the legal requirements regarding wastewater. This is the main goal to stay away from the danger of fines, prosecution, or even loss of their working permit. The thing that matters is that for those executing ISO certification, agreeing to enactment is the absolute minimum. Other deliberate moves will be made dependent on the need to secure the environment, to enhance previous performance, and to consider the invested parties needs and expectation."}],"$L10","$L11","$L12","$L13","$L14","$L15","$L16","$L17","$L18","$L19","$L1a","$L1b"]}],"$L1c"]}]}]
